Package edu.ncsu.csc216.tracker.requirement

Class Requirement

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.tracker.requirement.Requirement
  • public class Requirement
extends java.lang.Object
    Context and object class for the Requirement class. This class contains the finite state machine that command uses to change from state to state. Requirement handles the getter and setters for almost all fields
    Author:
    Troy Boone

      • Requirement

        public Requirement​(java.lang.String summary,
                   java.lang.String acceptanceTestId)
        Creates a new Requirement from a summary and acceptanceTestId. The ID is assigned to be the next number after the highest existing requirementId
        Parameters:
        summary - the requirements summary
        acceptanceTestId - the requirements acceptance test id

      • Requirement

        public Requirement​(edu.ncsu.csc216.tracker.xml.Req incoming)
        Creates a new Requirement from a Req object from RequirementTrackerXML. This will call each of the methods with the information got using the getters from the Req class and object
        Parameters:
        incoming - requirement being added
